OL,3,CHundreds of young people to play in
OL,4,CGaelic Football tournament in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FHundreds of young people are taking
OL,8,Fpart in a weekend of Irish sport in
OL,9,Fsouth Manchester.
OL,11,FThe Northern Community Gaelic Games is
OL,12,Fbringing Gaelic football to the city
OL,13,Fthis weekend.
OL,15,FOver two days at Broughton Park in
OL,16,Fsouth Manchester, more than 60 school
OL,17,Fteams and 115 club teams will compete
OL,18,Fin The Northern Community Gaelic
OL,19,FGames, which involves Gaelic football,
OL,20,Fhurling, and camogie.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
