PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781175772
OL,3,CHundreds of young people to play in
OL,4,CGaelic Football tournament in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FMatches organised by the Gaelic
OL,8,FAthletic Association (GAA) are going
OL,9,Fto run simultaneously on 17 pitches
OL,10,Ffrom early morning to late afternoon.
OL,12,FThe event also marks the opening of a
OL,13,Fnew GAA Centre of Excellence,
OL,14,Ffeaturing a pitch the same size as
OL,15,FCroke Park, Ireland's national stadium.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
