PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781175772
OL,3,CHundreds of young people to play in
OL,4,CGaelic Football tournament in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FColin McNamara of Lancashire GAA said
OL,8,F"On Friday, we have 60 school teams
OL,9,Fcoming down from all across
OL,10,FManchester, Scotland, Birmingham, all
OL,11,Fover. And then on Saturday, it's a
OL,12,Fbehemoth of a day with 115 club teams,
OL,13,F17 pitches going at once, all the way
OL,14,Ffrom 9:30 to 5 o'clock."
OL,16,FFor many participants, Gaelic games
OL,17,Fare a vital connection to their Irish
OL,18,Froots.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
