OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781175772
OL,3,CHundreds of young people to play in
OL,4,CGaelic Football tournament in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FStudents from Blessed Thomas Holford
OL,8,FSchool in Altrincham, one of the few
OL,9,Fschools in the northwest to offer
OL,10,FGaelic football as part of the
OL,11,Fcurriculum, spoke about growing up
OL,12,Fimmersed in the sport.
OL,14,FOne student said: "My mum and dad grew
OL,15,Fup playing it, and we always had it on
OL,16,Fthe TV watching Derry,"
OL,26,@vD@SOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
