PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781175772
OL,3,CHundreds of young people to play in
OL,4,CGaelic Football tournament in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FWhile many players have Irish links,
OL,8,Fthe games are not just for those of
OL,9,FIrish descent.
OL,11,FSean Hopkins, President of Britain GAA
OL,12,Fsaid "The game is for everyone.
OL,14,F"This year, the percentage of
OL,15,Fhomegrown players is over 40%. It's
OL,16,Freally taken off in schools, clubs,
OL,17,Fand universities throughout the whole
OL,18,Fcountry."
OL,20,FExcitement is high as the build-up
OL,21,Fcontinues among the young players.
OL,26,@tD@FOUvD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
