OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781175772
OL,3,CHundreds of young people to play in
OL,4,CGaelic Football tournament in
OL,5,CManchester
OL,7,FAnother student said: "Getting to the
OL,8,Ffinal is great because you know your
OL,9,Fname's on the big pitch and
OL,10,Feverything, so it should be a good
OL,11,Ftime."
OL,13,FWith dignitaries from the UK and
OL,14,FIreland in attendance, the Northern
OL,15,FCommunity Gaelic Games offer a grand
OL,16,Fstage for young talent and celebrate
OL,17,FGAA sports in Britain.
OL,26,@oD@WOUsD@FO]
